---
// Sin imports de React ni Lucide
---

<section class="py-20 bg-[hsl(0_0%_100%)]">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-fade-in">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)] mb-4">
        Lo Que Dicen Nuestros Pacientes
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)]">
        Experiencias reales de quienes confiaron en nosotros
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div
        class="p-6 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_-5px_hsl(210_20%_20%_/_0.12)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] relative"
        style="animation-delay: 0ms;"
      >
        <!-- Quote Icon (SVG inline) -->
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="40"
          height="40"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="h-10 w-10 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.2)] absolute top-4 right-4"
        >
          <path d="M3 21c3 0 7-2 7-5a4 4 0 0 0-8-2 1 1 0 0 1-1-1V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2c4 0 8 2 8 6a5 5 0 0 1-10 3v1a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H3z"/>
          <path d="M15 21c3 0 7-2 7-5a4 4 0 0 0-8-2 1 1 0 0 1-1-1V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2c4 0 8 2 8 6a5 5 0 0 1-10 3v1a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6z"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)] leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
            "Gracias a su enfermera, mi recuperación tras la lipo fue tranquila y sin complicaciones. ¡Totalmente recomendado!"
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] pt-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)]">
              Ana M.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)]">
              Girón
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div
        class="p-6 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_-5px_hsl(210_20%_20%_/_0.12)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] relative"
        style="animation-delay: 100ms;"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="40"
          height="40"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="h-10 w-10 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.2)] absolute top-4 right-4"
        >
          <path d="M3 21c3 0 7-2 7-5a4 4 0 0 0-8-2 1 1 0 0 1-1-1V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2c4 0 8 2 8 6a5 5 0 0 1-10 3v1a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H3z"/>
          <path d="M15 21c3 0 7-2 7-5a4 4 0 0 0-8-2 1 1 0 0 1-1-1V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2c4 0 8 2 8 6a5 5 0 0 1-10 3v1a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6z"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)] leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
            "Como familiar de un adulto mayor, me da tranquilidad saber que está en manos profesionales y humanas."
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] pt-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)]">
              Carlos R.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)]">
              Floridablanca
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div
        class="p-6 hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_-5px_hsl(210_20%_20%_/_0.12)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 animate-slide-up border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] relative"
        style="animation-delay: 200ms;"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          width="40"
          height="40"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="h-10 w-10 text-[hsl(205_65%_35%_/_0.2)] absolute top-4 right-4"
        >
          <path d="M3 21c3 0 7-2 7-5a4 4 0 0 0-8-2 1 1 0 0 1-1-1V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2c4 0 8 2 8 6a5 5 0 0 1-10 3v1a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H3z"/>
          <path d="M15 21c3 0 7-2 7-5a4 4 0 0 0-8-2 1 1 0 0 1-1-1V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2c4 0 8 2 8 6a5 5 0 0 1-10 3v1a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6z"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <p class="text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)] leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
            "Excelente servicio y muy económico comparado con otras opciones. La enfermera fue muy atenta y profesional."
          </p>
          <div class="border-t border-[hsl(210_20%_90%)] pt-4">
            <p class="font-semibold text-[hsl(210_20%_20%)]">
              María P.
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[hsl(210_15%_45%)]">
              Bucaramanga
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fade-in {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes slide-up {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fade-in 0.6s ease-out forwards;
  }
  .animate-slide-up {
    animation: slide-up 0.6s ease-out forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
</style>